    "In [23], a novel FL framework named federated model components self-attention (FedMCSA) is proposed to facilitate collaboration between clients with similar models.",
    "In this way, the personalized FL framework can adaptively update models and handle non-IIDness.",
    "Regularization methodsWe summarize federated learning algorithms with additional regularization terms to client learning objectives or server aggregation formulas.",
    "One category is to add local constraints for clients.",
    "FedProx [26] adds proximal terms to clients' objectives to regularize local training and ensure convergence in the non-IID setting."
  ],
